XCursor Pro is modern, simple and elegant cursor theme for Linux and Windows. This cursor theme is built with [b][url=https://github.com/ful1e5/clickgen]clickgen[/url][/b] and render with the [b][url=https://github.com/puppeteer/puppeteer/]puppeteer[/url][/b].

Available Sizes: 22, 24, 28, 32, 40, 48, 56, 64, 72, 80, 88, 96
Latest build: check [url=https://github.com/ful1e5/XCursor-pro/actions]Actions[/url][/b] tab on GitHub.
Release Notification: [url=https://twitter.com/ful1e5]@ful1e5[/url]
Check for customize the cursor size: [url=https://github.com/ful1e5/XCursor-pro/tree/main#manual-build]README.md#manual-build[/url]

